{"tid":511522,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文]終於見識到籃球撚有幾咁戇鳩...","createTime":"2017-12-27T14:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T20:26:43.000Z","uid":65191,"like":2095,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"d876e0ff6b1ac124938f9f28082fa470e02187d6","tid":511522,"uid":65191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"話說小弟係做緊待應既<br />\n咁今日有個男+女就入黎食飯 望落去廿歲頭到...<br />\n咁個男仔都成身籃球裝扮,應該岩岩打完波..<br />\n戇鳩既事就發生..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男仔點完餐之後..係咁係張台度做射波姿勢..維持左幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同D同事都笑撚到仆街..個女仔應該覺得個男仔好型,全程係咁望<br />\n戇鳩既事仲未發生完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男仔行出黎去洗手間,咁我地鋪頭吊高左D聖誕燈飾既<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌!你!老!母</span></span>,佢無撚啦啦<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路行一路跳高係咁掂D聖誕燈飾</span></span>,我諗佢係扮緊拍藍板<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大佬呀,大庭廣眾,戇鳩還戇鳩,真係唔好咁撚戇鳩好嘛?<br />\n做多左啦,籃球撚</span></span>"},{"pid":"6acc0b329ad5d0ae221fca22c0b94f1a144308bc","tid":511522,"uid":29523,"like":191,"dislike":415,"score":-224,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"一碌鳩打全球人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e01a7754fea43525a652dc679816b1e0148d7a","tid":511522,"uid":99968,"like":374,"dislike":10,"score":364,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑之前見到個籃球撚係度扮射波 真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f891ce8e1440cd5b9be6982b442a32533e39b1","tid":511522,"uid":50779,"like":4,"dislike":35,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e568a3e7a2