<blockquote>話說小弟係做緊待應既<br />\n咁今日有個男+女就入黎食飯 望落去廿歲頭到...<br />\n咁個男仔都成身籃球裝扮,應該岩岩打完波..<br />\n戇鳩既事就發生..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男仔點完餐之後..係咁係張台度做射波姿勢..維持左幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同D同事都笑撚到仆街..個女仔應該覺得個男仔好型,全程係咁望<br />\n戇鳩既事仲未發生完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男仔行出黎去洗手間,咁我地鋪頭吊高左D聖誕燈飾既<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌!你!老!母</span></span>,佢無撚啦啦<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路行一路跳高係咁掂D聖誕燈飾</span></span>,我諗佢係扮緊拍藍板<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大佬呀,大庭廣眾,戇鳩還戇鳩,真係唔好咁撚戇鳩好嘛?<br />\n做多左啦,籃球撚</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你地起度笑9人既時候，籃球撚已經連條女個屎眼都玩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eabc0d0cd54b93c23a4cc18431488bc36d5737","tid":511522,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c72d3a27d1e8b720fc9e4167f355757bd41a0b0","tid":511522,"uid":13555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"足撚係咪淨係識踩籃撚擦存在感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a100d3ab147701ee09f191343c81857347fbe90e","tid":511522,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"我以前讀中學嗰陣都試過係走廊行行下<br />\n無啦啦同班嘅籃波撚衝埋黎扮走籃又假動作轉身咁<br />\n真係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6287f6d08bdfc697eb4382c91940e2a68c5d930b","tid":511